BA_ "Description" SG_ 65 HKBD_Typ2 "Bit0 (Mode Def Type):0 ? Symbol Type/1 ? Arrow Type
Bit1 (Air Purifier Button):0 - None/1 - AIR PURIFIER BUTTON APPLIED
Bit2 (Haptic):0 - None/1 - Applied 
Bit3 (Multi Auto Button Type) :  0 - Push / 1 - Tumbler 
Bit4~ 5 (Climate OSD UI Type) : 0 - None (Basic UI Type) / 1 - (TEMP-Blower - Mode - Temp) / 2 - (Temp - Mode (Auto) - Blower - Temp) / 3 - Reserved 
Bit6~7 (Blower Button Type) : 0 - None / 1 - Blower down type / 2 - blower down off type / 3 - Invalid";
