BA_ "Description" SG_ 70 HKBD_SwBtnTyp "Each bit for button type is defined as
0-None/1-Hardkey/2-Touch(Used Beep)/3-Touch(Not Used Beep)
Bit 0~1 (Temp Button)/Bit 2~3 (Blower Button)/Bit 4~5 (Mode Button)/
Bit 6~7 (Auto Button)/Bit 8~9 (A/C Button)/Bit 10~11 (Def Button)/
Bit 12~13 (Intake Button)/Bit 14~15 (Sync Button)/Bit 16~17 (RrDef Button)/
Bit 18~19 (DrOnly Button)/Bit 20~21 (AirCln Button)/Bit 22~23 (StHeatVnt Button)/
Bit 24~25 (StrWhlHeat Button)/Bit 26~27 (FrWndShldHt Button)/
Bit 28~29 (Diffuser Button)/Bit 30~31 (OFF Button)/Bit 32~33 (Climate Button)
Bit 34~35 (FrRrTgl Button)
Bit36~37 (SmartZone Button) : 0 ? None / 1 ? HardKey / 2 ? Touch(Used Beep) / 3 ? Touch (Not Used Beep)
Bit 38~39 : Reserved";
